sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/ODH Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>Controller
    participant PVC as PersistentVolumeClaim
    participant Deployment as TrustyAI Deployment
    participant Service as ClusterIP Service
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ServiceCA as Service CA
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (User)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>(Internal)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create PVC<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>PVC: Provision Storage

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Deployment: Create Pods

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Service: Create Service

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Route: Create Route

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)

    ServiceCA->>Deployment: Provision TLS Certificates<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: InferenceService Integration

    Operator->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: InferenceService List

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService env<br/>MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Deployment: Update InferenceService

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: External Access to TrustyAI Service

    User->>Route: HTTPS Request<br/>443/TCP TLS1.2+
    Route->>Service: Forward (Reencrypt)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Service->>Deployment: OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over Deployment: OAuth Proxy validates token

    Deployment->>Deployment: Forward to TrustyAI Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Deployment-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Service: Scrape /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Service->>Deployment: Forward to TrustyAI<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Deployment-->>Service: Metrics Data
    Service-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics

    Prometheus->>Operator: Scrape /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator-->>Prometheus: Operator Metrics
